OL,3,CPolice to roll out London's first
OL,4,Cpermanent facial recognition cameras
OL,6,FPolice are rolling out London's first
OL,7,Fpermanent facial recognition cameras.
OL,8,FThe live facial recognition (LFR)
OL,9,Fcameras, aimed at helping police catch
OL,10,Fsuspects faster, will be installed in
OL,11,FCroydon, south London.
OL,13,FThe cameras scan faces and check them
OL,14,Fagainst a database of known criminals.
OL,15,FAnyone not matched is automatically
OL,16,Fdeleted.
OL,18,FThey'll be fixed to lampposts or
OL,19,Fbuildings and will only operate when
OL,20,Fofficers are available to monitor them.
