OL,3,CPolice to roll out London's first
OL,4,Cpermanent facial recognition cameras
OL,6,FPolice have already been operating
OL,7,Fmobile facial recognition cameras from
OL,8,Fvans, allowing them to be deployed
OL,9,Fanywhere in the city.
OL,11,FCroydon Council Community Safety
OL,12,FCabinet Member Ola Kolade believes the
OL,13,Fuse of this technology will improve
OL,14,Fsafety in the area.
