OL,3,CPolice to roll out London's first
OL,4,Cpermanent facial recognition cameras
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News London, Cllr
OL,7,FKolade said: "The safety of residents
OL,8,Fin Croydon is of paramount importance
OL,9,Fto the council and its partners, and
OL,10,Fwhen we previously piloted this, we
OL,11,Fsaw lots of support from community
OL,12,Fgroups and residents.
OL,14,F"The point of this new system is for
OL,15,Fit to be targeted; it works by looking
OL,16,Fat people who are on the police's
OL,17,Flist, and it enables the police to
OL,18,Fhave those conversations."
