OL,3,CPolice to roll out London's first
OL,4,Cpermanent facial recognition cameras
OL,6,FRebecca Vincent from the Big Brother
OL,7,FWatch group has raised concerns about
OL,8,Fthe facial recognition technology.
OL,10,FVincent said to ITV News London: "This
OL,11,Fis a massive expansion of the
OL,12,Fsurveillance state. Anybody coming
OL,13,Fthrough the Croydon town centre will
OL,14,Fhave their faces scanned whether they
OL,15,Fare suspected of any crime or not.
OL,17,F"This new rollout is alarming and is
OL,18,Fanother step towards a dystopian
OL,19,Fnightmare."
